data.description: THE OPEN-CONCEPT DESIGN MAKES THIS HOME FEEL AND LOOK SPACIOUS. This beauty is a SINGLE STORY WITH SOLAR.. Inside has 3 bedrooms/2 bathrooms. The gorgeous kitchen features mocha color cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops with rolling matching island for more counter space. 2 bedrooms upfront with a guest bathroom. Plenty of linen/storage closets. Main bedroom has a private bathroom with a glass enclosure shower and a private door for the toilet area. Walk in closet also has its own linen closet. Whole house fan. Recessed lighting in the family room. Tankless water heater in a 2 car garage. Also the  backyard has a nice flower bed area along with a doggie run on the other side of the house. Other side of the yard has a concrete slab to store your bins and the  front yard has nice landscaping with handrail. Buyer to assume Solar lease for approx. 50.00 a month. This master planned community with amenities that include a Junior Olympic Fitness Pool, Spa, Resort Pool, Spray Park, clubhouse, event room with terrace and event lawn, Outdoor Dining Room with Fire Pit, Half-court basketball court and Outdoor BBQ area. Close to the 15 freeway or Ortega Highway. NEW FLOORING is on the whole house and is ready for showings. Appliances are negotiable and the rolling island stays with home. Seller is motivated  --
